    <div class="column large-6">
      <h2 class="section__title"><span class="section__number">01.</span> The Challenge</h1>

      <p>Historically, traditional lenders and banks can be  very slow, inefficient, and biased when it comes to approving loans. Additionally, they were hesitant to invest after the real estate crash in 2008 which left  communities across the country devastated.</p>

      <p>Our client came to us with an idea, basic site, and the data for a real estate crowdfunding platform that would be an inclusive solution that would allow investors to quickly assign risk profiles and reduce the time and cost of traditional loan methods. We had less than 3 months to complete the project.</p>

       <div class="details">My Role: Lead Designer</div>

       <p>As the sole designer, I managed client expectations, researched end users, completed the UI Design for the marketing website and platform, as well as completed the frontend implementation using HTML, CSS and Javascript while making sure the site was mobile responsive and accessible.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="column large-6">
